Acked-by: Sam Ravnborg <sam@ravnborg.org>
Signed-off-by: Robert Foss <robert.foss@linaro.org>
Link: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/msgid/20210621125518.13715-3-laurent.pinchart@ideasonboard.com

